Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:53.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Boss Luffy Returns! Is it a Dream\Nor Reality? Lottery Ruckus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Grand Jipang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It resembles a certain era of\Na certain country quite a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, well, let's not get too specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although there were some troubles last year
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after some rogues wandered into this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,peace reigns over this land for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are fully enjoying peace\Nand spending cheerful days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! You're the ones who bumped into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, yeah. Oh, shoot! I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Dr. Bluenose\Nhasn't shown up lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't know what's going on,\Nbut he seems quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You guys are from that clown group!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are dangerous.\NThey're always hanging out with Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are making a\Nracket out in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying when you're\Nthe one who came in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here to pick a fight, I'm up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's get out of here.\NHe doesn't seem to be here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. Looks like we were given a bum steer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're leaving now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, we don't get decent customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Scatter some salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, Onami?\NWere there more annoying customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use saying anything\Nto someone who's oblivious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss. Where's your payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! That's right! I have to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Put it on my tab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Maybe I should\Nreport this to the police soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought,\Ndon't worry about it, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll keep coming back anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, come to think of it,\Nsalt is expensive these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, he just happened\Nto be in that eatery, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he's gotten in our way yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrrgh! How irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came to this town,\Nour earnings have dropped considerably!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should go to a different town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You idiot!\N--Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I, the great Buggy,\Njust get my butt whipped and leave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's saying I got my butt whipped?!\NI never did, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna slice you into three and eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mood is quite nasty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really getting into the habit of losing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we'd better find him quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and shake him down, or we won't\Nbe able to welcome in the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orika! How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be getting quite a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate some rice porridge earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orika, Pepper and the others\Nare worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Rika. I'll watch pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops tells me to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's warm on the southern islands! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Pineapple-ple! Their heads\Nare nice and warm! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ They're all idiots! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the second verse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's cold on the northern islands! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Freezing, real freezing!\NTheir heads are shivering... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A horse...? No, it's not a horse, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what it is! It's called a camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look very tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Does it hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have a slight fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, could you carry him to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad leaving him here.\NHe seems to be hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no problem, but with pops, too,\Nyour place is too small for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be okay to just leave him by\Nthe well at the row house on the back alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he's hungry, then we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, don't just bring anything to our place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running a business, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Your place\Nis pretty empty anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Bluenose isn't around when we need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave things to Orika.\NShe's used to taking care of the sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought a camel would be cooler than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble, Boss!\NHm? What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orika took him in and is nursing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orika is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what's the\Nmatter, Usopp? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! There's trouble at Orika's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come with me right away, Boss!\N--What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, walk briskly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you were\Nhiding in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that you could outrun us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it. He's a sick man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! He's a guarantor of a loan.\NIf you wanna complain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do so to the guy who skipped town,\Nforcing the deed on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just collecting the money as agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't bother with her! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You think\Nyou can get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You guys are the ones\Nwho're doing something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the deed.\NCome back when you get a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deed for such a large\Namount can't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still gonna take pops, I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You blockhead! There's this\Nthing called interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make him work for\Nthe rest of his life to repay us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for you, a policeman, to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Let pops go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Orika!\N--Wh-Who's this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. We'll take you too and sell you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rika!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Billy Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit! How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! All right! Get out of\Nhere and don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to think that clown would\Nback down without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll work out okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds terrible.\NSo what happened to pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's resting at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost better, but he tries\Nto push himself and go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I scolded him, saying that\Nhe should lay down and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can twist even pops\Naround your little finger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Camel got his energy back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Good timing. I made his food\Nusing leftovers. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Sanji? Isn't my food ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate just a bit ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you go!\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're making some tasty-looking food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are expensive dishes\Nfor delivery, you damn jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Camel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna eat? I'm sure you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't eat, you can't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want them? Then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I made these dishes using\Nexpensive food! They're for delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna slice you into three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he can make\Nsuch tasty food with leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I'm mad! I'm seriously\Ngonna slice you into three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sanji-san! Please don't blame Mr. Camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he ate those\Nbecause they looked tastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Who do you think\Nyou are?! You're just a camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sanji-san, Onami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onami, you sure are generous today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd have beaten\Nthe crap out of the person by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm thinking this\Nmight be some sort of turn of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This. Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a Year-End lottery ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lottery ticket? What does\Nthat have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:24.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Camel"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Camel, 1356?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think it might be good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the drawing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Usopp to go there and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third prize! Camel, 1356!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A million Ryo-Berry third prize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I checked many times!\NThere's no mistaking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true...? It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We can now welcome in\Nthe new year without any problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be out of our desperate\Nfinancial situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my bills will all be wiped out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you who hit the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were a good-luck camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you eat whatever you like,\Nsince this is definitely thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could eat the lottery ticket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out! Spit it out!\NA million Ryo-Berries! Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must really like expensive stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Spit it out! A million Ryo-Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Camel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good-luck camel? What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to check just in case...\NThey sure are connected by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I wish they wouldn't\Npull me into things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to call me out so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to join hands, we have to settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been having a hard time with that tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good chance.\NYou don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Commissioner, it's okay\Nto flashily get rid of Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be a big deal for a\Npoliceman or two to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it's he who's at fault this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gulp.\N--That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I get rid of him, you and I will\Ncontrol this town and do as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Confectionery\NCarefully Produced"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are golden-colored confectioneries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as bad as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Cabaji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Seems like it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that, you moron-ji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so busy! I'm so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's trouble! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Boss out for delivery with that camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad timing! Orika got\Nkidnapped by the Buggy Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she got caught by them\Nout of the blue on her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they were after Orika from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Ah! You guys are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay with you? That girl\Nwill be sold off to repay the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say about Orika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be leaving the harbor soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be on your way to rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an important piece\Nof bait to trick Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we're collecting\Nmoney based on a deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he tries to raise his hand against\Nme in front of the commissioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can immediately get fired and be exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I'll get\Nmoney from selling you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! What're you gonna\Ndo with Orika?! Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Straw Hat. I'm taking this girl\Nas collateral for that man's loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to butt in\Nthis time! Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Help me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You interfered with us, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A policeman beating up commoners\Nover personal matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think about\Nhis act?! Commissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! The commissioner?\NWhat's he doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just like our boss, Koza-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a town commissioner and\Nthe top person in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you'd use violence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,towards commoners who\Nare not at fault like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a commissioner, I cannot overlook this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy! I hereby strip you of\Nyour role as policeman. You're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this country immediately\Nand never set foot here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your punishment for meddling\Nin our business all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, then hurry up and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to leave here\Njust because I tried to save Orika?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talking like that, you blockhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unseemly, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to talk your way out\Nafter everything you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can immediately call the constables in\Nand have them arrest you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should\Nbe arrested, Commissioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A town commissioner joining hands\Nwith criminals? It's quite inexcusable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm removing you from your position right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk like a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you say that knowing that\NI'm the North Town Commissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How insolent! Kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the daughter of Shogun Cobra! Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being disrespectful! Kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Vivi!\N--Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was really you, Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... what's the princess doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My investigation has shown\Nthat you took a bribe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are working with the\Nclown to trick Boss Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Yes ma'am" her, you stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Now that it's come\Nto this, I'll flashily withdraw,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,taking the loan collateral with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like I said...!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orika can't be collateral for the loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she isn't pops' daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--This way! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called him pops!\NThey're clearly father and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Hey, Boss! I brought him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you collapsed. Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things just aren't the same\Nat Pinwheel without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What?\N--Let's have a drink together again soon, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, everyone calls him "pops."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing odd about\NOrika calling him that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was sleeping at her house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops made his cold worse and\Ncollapsed the other day on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Orika happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the kind of girl who can't\Njust leave someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this girl has nothing to do with the loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it now? Then I'm\Ngonna do it this year again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get blown away, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lord's pet?! This camel is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Lashes has been lost for a while,\Nso we've all been looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reward is a million Ryo-Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll definitely pay the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this is becoming a routine,\Nit's hard to tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it Orika who deserves the credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Let's share it. We all\Ntook care of him, so... Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I love you, Orika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's have some fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll celebrate pops'\Ncomplete recovery as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what're these decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?! Today's called\NChristmas Eve in foreign countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a joyous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be cheery like\Nthis once in a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Onami-san. Can I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?\N--Orika took in someone who\Ncollapsed on the street again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already brought him here and\Nhe's outside. Can we bring him inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collapsed on the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, monk. If a foreign celebration is\Nokay with you, why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got lots of yummy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Let's really\Nwhoop it up, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, where's Dr. Bluenose?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's still busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he can understand animal languages,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lashes' problem could've been solved\Nright away if he had been around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, today is a\Nreally busy day for reindeers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! There's trouble! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, there's always trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, eat a rice cake or something\Nand calm down, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna have a\Nrice cake tossing event at the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one of them will have\Nan amazing treasure inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how big of an uproar it'll cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. Our lord is asking us to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that'd be a lot of work. Hey, we are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Big Rice Cake Tossing Race\Nat the Castle! Red Nose's Plot"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:23:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a policeman!!
